This is a Java based web application using Play framework.
=================================
This app is developed to work as a mediator between any LMS system and LTI tool.

This app takes care of secure communication between different LMSs such as Canvas and BlackBoard and LTI tools as well as taking care of the 
authentication using OAuth.

Controllers
===========

- HomeController.java:

contains the methods related to assignment creation/edit/deletion.

-SubmissionController.java:

contains the method related to store student submission for any codecheck/interactive problem

-GradeSubmitterController.java:

contains the method related to generating the XML file to pass the grades back to LMS as well as sending the file to LMS.

Models
===========
-Problem.java

-Assignment.java

-Submission.java
